    DEVELOPMENT SERVERS - BASTION (Phase 1)

Welcome to the PyTorch Development Server Platform bastion!

🚀 Phase 1 - Bastion Infrastructure Testing
   This is a proof-of-concept environment.

📋 Available Commands:
   devctl status     - Show environment status
   devctl info       - Show available commands  
   devctl test-k8s   - Test Kubernetes connectivity
   devctl --help     - Full command help

🔧 What's Working:
   ✓ SSH access to bastion
   ✓ Basic CLI environment
   ✓ Kubernetes connectivity
   ✓ User namespace assignment

⚡ Coming in Phase 2:
   • Server creation (devctl create)
   • PyTorch development containers
   • Distributed training support
   • Full operator with CRDs

📚 Documentation: https://docs.company.com/pytorch-dev-operator
🐛 Issues: https://github.com/company/pytorch-dev-operator/issues

